OOC: Don't worry Scorpius, you'll catch on.  LOL! Soulstice, you had my sides 
splitting!  Also, it's Soulstice's turn with Abominus.

:::The Destrocons/Battera:::

::They walk back to their quarters::
~~~~~
::Battera gets Dachande's message.  her eyes go wide and her jaw drops::
Battera: Oh, Primus, Cybershark's back!  But where did he go? Why did he go? 
Stop asking yourself questions Battera and go to him! Ahh, i'm talking to 
myself! I must be going crazy.
::She slaps herself, and breaks the window of her quarters, and starts flying 
to Dachande's coordinates::

--part1_8d.5bf91fd.281b9af9_boundary
